channel.title: PLEASE HELP! - Stuck on 3rd level
channel.description: On my own server, whenever I log on, even with a new account, I always appear to be on the 3rd level. The global objects appear on my level but no npc's or other players do. I have also edited the character's level to zero, but he always stays on the 3rd level. Could someone please help me with a ::ground code or something like that, because I am really screwed. :(
